## interruption and signal
sigaction
setitimer
ptrace

## Virtual memory ##
mprotect - set protection on a region of memory
mtrace, muntrace - malloc tracing

## IPC ##
### socket ###
socket()
setsockopt()
bind()
listen() if TCP
send
sendto
sendmsg
SSL_write   /* SSL connection */

### async monitoring ###
select
poll
epoll  /* Linux */
kqueue(kevent)  /* FreeBSD */


## profiling ##
profil  (gprof toolkit)
